<episodedetails><title>Remaking the Middle East: The U.S., Israel &amp; Iran (2026)</title><plot>The road to war with Iran, the U.S. and Israeli roles, and the stakes for the region. This is an updated presentation of the July 25, 2025 program, which traces Benjamin Netanyahu's long campaign to defeat Iran and his relations with the U.S. over peace and the regime's nuclear ambitions.</plot></episodedetails>